channel.title: Rushing Team?
channel.description: I'm not a fan of rushing but anyone want to rush? Looking for a team with even splits. Must be within 102-106 not including summon. 3 People must have Ancient mace 1 with either claws(preferred), ags or korasi Void would be nice. Good stats aren't required. The reasoning why ancient mace is to smite there prot item :) http://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Ancient_mace 52 Prayer is required. I'm using Korasi + elite void veng etc so I should hit a nice 500 most likely.
